WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:05.200
I see the sun arising upon Africa today.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:08.719
I see the fire and the glory.

00:00:08.719 --> 00:00:12.663
I see the rays of the sun shining upon the people.

00:00:14.376 --> 00:00:18.800
I see the African people with their faces looking toward the sun.

00:00:22.064 --> 00:00:28.571
In this vision, I see it is olive oil—the Holy Ghost oil running down their faces.

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:40.680
They are dressed in African garb with tribal beads.

00:00:59.999 --> 00:01:06.217
There is red on these outfits and they have headdresses on.

00:01:06.217 --> 00:01:17.840
As they are looking toward the sun, I see a new oil running down their faces, and there is a glory on them.

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:29.344
There is nothing around but dirt and these heights, but as this glory is falling, oil is saturating them.

00:01:29.344 --> 00:01:39.508
It is like whenever you dump oil, it spreads, and the glory of the Lord is coming upon the African people.

00:01:59.302 --> 00:01:59.588
I see them jumping and putting their chests out, making a noise and popping their chests back.

00:01:59.588 --> 00:02:09.623
They have beads and paint on them, but there is olive oil coming down on them.

00:02:09.623 --> 00:02:16.160
He has not forgotten you today.

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:21.120
Many think, 'Where is the revival for Africa?

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:26.840
Where is the coming of the King?

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:29.250
Where is the Lord?

00:02:29.250 --> 00:02:33.360
There has been so much drought here.

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:44.346
' I see the drought, but I hear the sound of an abundance of rain, even down to the Congo.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:47.680
That is what He just said.

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:54.080
Amidst great persecution, you are going to see creative miracles.

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:09.120
This is going to be a wave.

00:03:29.744 --> 00:03:30.248
A wave will come and pull, and another wave will come right on the heels of the creative miracles.

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:39.800
You are about to see a wave of the glory upon this world.

00:03:53.456 --> 00:03:53.720
It will come in waves; it will look like one is receding, but another wave will come.

00:03:53.720 --> 00:03:57.568
In the wave of this glory, I see body parts.

00:03:58.240 --> 00:04:05.620
The wave comes in and it recedes back, but before it even has time to recede back, another glory wave comes in.

00:04:05.620 --> 00:04:13.900
In this wave are eyes, ears, hands, and feet; body parts from My reserves are coming unto thee.

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:26.640
There will be creative miracles flowing in Africa and America as you yield to it.

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:38.360
I see a Holy Ghost wave of glory flowing in South America and hitting all out in the bush.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:05:05.240
You will see the glory of the Lord, and I will wash it over the people.

00:05:10.710 --> 00:05:11.250
It will look like a washing and a flow.

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:15.635
It will flow unlike anything you have ever seen before.

00:05:15.635 --> 00:05:23.030
I hear the Lord say, 'It will be a flow.

00:05:23.030 --> 00:05:42.400
' I see the eyes, ears, toes, and what you have been believing for from these great silos, for I am emptying them out.

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:53.439
I hear Him say, 'What new do you need to hear?

00:06:01.795 --> 00:06:03.903
I have reserved it for today, for a great move of My presence will be upon My people.

00:06:09.813 --> 00:06:18.560
I will empty the reserves, for there is no need for it here; this is what I call, and it will draw you near.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:28.960
For it is My goodness that will bring them to repentance.

00:06:48.217 --> 00:06:48.663
My goodness will pass through.

00:06:56.366 --> 00:07:01.170
It will be My goodness and My mercy that you will see—something you did not earn and did not deserve.

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:14.169
' I hear the sound of an abundance of rain, for it will be the glory.

00:07:14.169 --> 00:07:18.400
Unto Him be all the glory.

00:07:20.590 --> 00:07:24.619
I am emptying My silos; they are dumping them out.

00:07:35.952 --> 00:07:36.544
It will come in on the waves—a wave of glory.

00:07:36.544 --> 00:07:43.360
I see black arms, white arms, brown arms, and yellow arms.

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:52.060
Creative miracles: blue eyes, black eyes, brown eyes, and green eyes.

00:07:52.060 --> 00:08:03.560
As you walk in My authority, there will be healings of hearts, livers, and intestines.

00:08:11.648 --> 00:08:11.936
I see brand new colons.

00:08:11.936 --> 00:08:20.759
You might have a colostomy bag, but He is going to restore back what the cankerworm ate.

00:08:28.604 --> 00:08:28.862
He said, 'There will be no sick among you.

00:08:28.862 --> 00:08:38.800
' Just like the children of Israel, they left with no sickness or disease.

00:08:47.620 --> 00:08:47.990
You will walk in the same; it will be a type and shadow.

00:08:47.990 --> 00:08:55.131
This is an outpouring over Africa, South America, and America.

00:08:55.131 --> 00:08:59.939
He says, 'America, get out of the thinking of the natural.

00:08:59.939 --> 00:09:14.011
' If you resist this—I see America and Africa—it is happening like ripe cherries off a tree for the people who would just believe.

00:09:14.011 --> 00:09:20.948
He says, 'But you come up to how you think it should be.

00:09:20.948 --> 00:09:28.133
' America tries to block it like with a dam because of the traditions of man.

00:09:28.133 --> 00:09:35.600
Get out of the natural thinking; come up higher with Me.

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:38.862
Do not be a dam; be a river.

00:09:38.862 --> 00:09:44.160
Let the Holy Ghost flow like He can in Africa.

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:46.800
Let Him flow through America.

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:49.371
I see the waves of glory.

00:10:03.350 --> 00:10:03.600
Before a wave is able to come back, another wave will come on top of it, for I am emptying My silos.

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:11.280
This is the great finale He has for us—the greatest finale of all.

00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.279
His goodness will be displayed upon everyone.

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:17.519
His goodness and mercy will follow all over you.

00:10:17.884 --> 00:10:19.342
I have the greatest treasures for you.

00:10:19.342 --> 00:10:30.311
Do not become accustomed to what He is about to do, taking it for granted when you hear about someone else getting a blessing.

00:10:30.311 --> 00:10:33.200
Everything is precious that you will see.

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:47.039
This is what Kathryn Kuhlman desired to see.

00:10:47.039 --> 00:10:56.480
I heard Him just say this is what Kathryn Kuhlman desired to see, and she did not see the full manifestation of it.

00:10:56.480 --> 00:11:02.720
She is standing in the great cloud of witnesses.

00:11:02.720 --> 00:11:09.726
She is watching, wearing the same outfit she had on earth with the bell sleeves.

00:11:09.726 --> 00:11:15.164
She is looking out, anticipating what she is about to see.

00:11:15.164 --> 00:11:23.289
Isn't it amazing the Lord allows me to see the ones who have gone before us?

00:11:23.289 --> 00:11:25.543
They are anticipating this glorious outpouring.

00:11:25.543 --> 00:11:31.672
Kim Clement was there, and now I see Kathryn Kuhlman looking over a portal.

00:11:31.672 --> 00:11:42.360
There is an edge with grass and Kathryn Kuhlman is sitting right there.

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:55.980
There is a wall that looks like a well, or like a TV screen, but it is not.

00:11:55.980 --> 00:12:00.126
It is a well of water.

00:12:02.036 --> 00:12:09.850
I can see a well of water, and they come up and they can see over into it.

00:12:09.850 --> 00:12:23.280
It's a round hole, a portal, showing glimpses of what's happening in certain parts of the earth, and they're able to see into it.

00:12:23.280 --> 00:12:34.600
It actually has bricks that are built up around it; it looks like a cobblestone well.

00:12:34.600 --> 00:12:37.485
Catherine is looking over this.

00:12:37.485 --> 00:12:44.034
There's green grass on this side, and she's looking over into it.

00:12:44.034 --> 00:12:52.880
It's like a picture show, but if you touched it, you could interrupt the water.

00:12:54.030 --> 00:13:05.530
You know how when you see your reflection in the water and if you touch it, it goes away until the water's calm again?

00:13:05.530 --> 00:13:06.660
It's like that.

00:13:06.660 --> 00:13:10.436
It's a well, and you can see into it.

00:13:11.307 --> 00:13:13.880
I can see her face looking into this.

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:25.899
She's looking over and watching, anticipating the greatest move of the Spirit of God that we've ever seen.

00:13:43.920 --> 00:13:44.384
They're all anticipating.

00:13:59.851 --> 00:14:00.309
The silos are being emptied.

00:14:04.800 --> 00:14:13.660
The angelic host are emptying the silos right now.

00:14:24.808 --> 00:14:25.136
The Lord said, 'Why do I have need of them here?

00:14:25.136 --> 00:14:27.760
I've saved them for today.

00:14:27.760 --> 00:14:29.400
' It's now.

00:14:29.400 --> 00:14:33.371
He saved them for this last show.

00:14:33.371 --> 00:14:38.160
This is the grand finale.

00:14:38.160 --> 00:14:43.907
When you get up here, they'll be empty.

00:14:59.199 --> 00:14:59.779
You'll see.

00:14:59.779 --> 00:15:02.880
Reach out by faith and receive.

00:15:02.880 --> 00:15:08.275
That's what I just heard him say.

00:15:08.275 --> 00:15:15.679
Reach out with simple faith as a child and receive.

00:15:15.679 --> 00:15:21.428
Don't think like an adult; think like a child.

00:15:21.428 --> 00:15:25.519
He said, 'Come to me as a child.

00:15:25.519 --> 00:15:35.623
Reach out by faith and receive just like a child would receive.

00:15:35.623 --> 00:15:40.100
' That's what I heard the Lord say.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:47.499
And I see these children; they're so easily able to receive it.

00:15:47.499 --> 00:15:50.789
They don't have any doubt.

00:15:50.789 --> 00:16:02.809
Doubt is taught because of life circumstances, but a child believes without doubt.

00:16:02.809 --> 00:16:04.468
They just believe.

00:16:04.468 --> 00:16:07.110
'We're going to get that for you.

00:16:07.110 --> 00:16:08.498
' 'Okay, Dad.

00:16:08.498 --> 00:16:10.297
' They just trust.

00:16:10.297 --> 00:16:17.142
He said, 'Come to me as the children would come to you.

00:16:17.142 --> 00:16:18.839
' Like trust.

00:16:18.839 --> 00:16:26.822
Disappointment comes in because you let them down, but I'm telling you, come to God like this child.

00:16:30.660 --> 00:16:30.890
I see the wave.

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:49.390
I hear the wave.

00:16:56.180 --> 00:16:56.550
And it will come on the hill with the greatest outpouring.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:04.410
This greatest well—I see people coming to Jesus.

00:17:04.410 --> 00:17:11.400
Remember even with Jesus, he didn't heal the saved; he healed the sinner.

00:17:21.439 --> 00:17:21.919
It's the goodness of God that brings men to repentance, and his goodness and mercy will flow over me.

00:17:28.023 --> 00:17:28.720
I see gold coins raining down.

00:17:44.560 --> 00:17:45.013
This represents finances—a supernatural outpouring of finances.

00:17:45.013 --> 00:17:47.999
My cup runneth over.

00:17:47.999 --> 00:17:52.514
I see plants and seeds you've sowed.

00:17:54.171 --> 00:17:56.491
The seeds you sowed will come to pass at last.

00:17:58.799 --> 00:17:59.172
The harvest is plentiful.

00:17:59.919 --> 00:18:05.410
The sacrificial seed you sowed will come to pass at last.

00:18:05.410 --> 00:18:07.618
Now I'm seeing Asia today.

00:18:22.400 --> 00:18:22.789
I'm over Asia.

00:18:25.120 --> 00:18:26.114
I just got taken from Africa.

00:18:38.670 --> 00:18:39.020
I'm in Asia and I see South Korea, the edge, Taiwan, and the edge of China.

00:18:39.020 --> 00:18:46.537
I see a glory wave just like I'm talking about over Africa and over Asia today.

00:18:46.537 --> 00:18:53.720
I see the waves of healings and manifestations over Asia, for I have not forgotten my Asians.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:19:03.870
A great move of my presence and the Spirit over Asia, South America, and these areas.

00:19:03.870 --> 00:19:08.960
You'll see it over South Korea.

00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:11.313
South Korea will be a hub.

00:19:28.011 --> 00:19:28.320
A major pillar of revival will spring forth from South Korea and it will spread throughout China, Vietnam, and all of Asia.

00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:43.600
A major move of God will spring forth from South Korea, for the Korean people are interceding and praying.

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:50.382
This great revival will be birthed out of prayer.

00:20:04.190 --> 00:20:04.580
I see a major rock.

00:20:04.580 --> 00:20:08.940
When you toss a rock into the water, it causes a wave.

00:20:08.940 --> 00:20:14.994
This is what's coming forth out of South Korea: a Holy Ghost rock.

00:20:14.994 --> 00:20:24.333
'Upon this rock, I will build my church, and the gates of hell will not prevail against it.

00:20:24.333 --> 00:20:27.581
' That's what he just said.

00:20:27.581 --> 00:20:28.788
It's over South Korea.

00:20:28.788 --> 00:20:34.400
As this goes, a wave of the glory through prayer.

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:40.559
It's going to Japan, North Korea, Taiwan—it's going all over.

00:20:49.371 --> 00:20:49.749
A wave goes all around in all directions.

00:20:49.749 --> 00:20:53.280
That's what's about to happen.

00:21:05.600 --> 00:21:05.966
It's here now; you just believe it.

00:21:05.966 --> 00:21:14.559
As this happens in South Korea, it even has an effect on Alaska and Hawaii—a tsunami wave of the glory.

00:21:14.559 --> 00:21:15.700
It's a hot spot.

00:21:19.299 --> 00:21:19.679
It will trickle even over into Russia, Eastern Russia.

00:21:22.128 --> 00:21:22.674
It affects China, Russia, and North Korea.

00:21:22.674 --> 00:21:32.034
This is the glory, birthed and fueled by prayer, fired by the Spirit, ignited with his glory.

00:21:32.034 --> 00:21:37.999
It will flow, the wave of the presence of the Lord.

00:21:50.799 --> 00:21:51.679
It shows the influence; it's so thick.

00:21:51.679 --> 00:21:54.960
I see fire, I see South Korea.

00:21:54.960 --> 00:22:03.529
The glory of the Lord is so thick it looks like walls.

00:22:03.529 --> 00:22:07.200
It's a saturating and soaking glory all throughout Asia.

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:12.159
You can walk inside of the glory of the Lord.

00:22:12.159 --> 00:22:19.220
When you walk into this glory, it's thick and you can remain in it.

00:22:19.220 --> 00:22:24.380
It's like pouring over that oil again.

00:22:24.380 --> 00:22:29.131
I see people laying prostrate all over the ground.

00:22:29.131 --> 00:22:34.373
Some have been laid out in the glory for days.

00:22:36.480 --> 00:22:42.159
The glory of the Lord is so heavy they'll be slain for a day or two.

00:22:42.159 --> 00:22:44.030
You're caught up in the presence.

00:22:44.030 --> 00:22:49.349
You don't need to eat or drink; you're in the glory.

00:22:49.349 --> 00:22:58.840
We've not experienced what we're about to experience with the goodness of God that brings man to repentance.

00:23:13.360 --> 00:23:13.600
It's going to change you from the inside out.

00:23:15.382 --> 00:23:19.840
A glory explosion with Shekinah glory—the weightiness of God.

00:23:23.253 --> 00:23:24.190
The Lord said it will go back to Brownsville.

00:23:24.190 --> 00:23:29.910
For those of you that got to experience Brownsville, he said it was a weightiness.

00:23:29.910 --> 00:23:32.690
But he said, 'Magnify it by ten.

00:23:32.690 --> 00:23:37.982
' Take what happened at Brownsville and magnify it by ten.

00:23:37.982 --> 00:23:41.250
We've never experienced what's about to happen.

00:23:41.250 --> 00:23:47.120
People will crawl out of bars, and it will radiate from these glory spots.

00:23:47.120 --> 00:23:50.526
One will be in Tennessee.

00:23:50.526 --> 00:23:54.040
I see Perry in Cleveland.

00:24:07.325 --> 00:24:07.668
It's right on the border.

00:24:08.696 --> 00:24:14.240
There's going to be a glory spot right where Harvest Church is, where Billy goes.

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:32.159
There's a glory spot there, and there will be one down at the Church of His Presence with Pastor John Kilpatrick.

00:24:32.159 --> 00:24:34.103
They are glory spots again.

00:24:34.606 --> 00:24:40.765
He says, 'I'm going to do a great thing in them.

00:24:40.765 --> 00:24:43.566
' I see John Kilpatrick and I see Perry.

00:24:48.656 --> 00:24:49.472
I see John Kilpatrick.

00:25:04.352 --> 00:25:05.087
I see the glory on John Kilpatrick.

00:25:05.087 --> 00:25:12.710
Again, there are things that He is working out in him.

00:25:12.710 --> 00:25:15.417
He's stirring up revival back in him.

00:25:18.799 --> 00:25:19.233
I see a cultivation happening in John.

00:25:19.233 --> 00:25:25.280
Pastor John, I see—like whenever you take and whip whipping cream—there's a whipping inside of him.

00:25:25.280 --> 00:25:28.679
He's stirring up inside of him again.

00:25:28.679 --> 00:25:34.960
And it's a cultivation inside of Pastor John Kilpatrick, like a stirring, a whipping like whipping cream.

00:25:34.960 --> 00:25:46.822
Like when you have a big bowl, but it's inside of him; He said He's cranking it.

00:25:46.822 --> 00:25:54.519
You know when you see those old Model T Fords and you have to crank them?

00:25:54.799 --> 00:26:03.226
The old Model T Ford you have to crank to start it again.

00:26:17.100 --> 00:26:17.520
And there's a starting up inside of him again of fanning the flame.

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:31.939
His youth is renewed like the eagles, and I'm going to give him a fountain of youth to finish the race.

00:26:31.939 --> 00:26:39.779
That's what the Holy Ghost said: 'I'm going to finish what I started in him.

00:26:39.779 --> 00:26:44.879
And I'm going to stir a new revival in John Kilpatrick again.

00:26:44.879 --> 00:26:48.480
I'm going to stir in him again.

00:26:48.480 --> 00:26:56.519
' It's going to be a whipping, a stir.

00:26:56.519 --> 00:27:00.960
I'm going to give him a fresh anointing again.

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:11.039
I can see Pastor John Kilpatrick and He's going to give him a fresh fire.

00:27:11.039 --> 00:27:20.800
He's dealing with his weight and his heart, cleansing his arteries, and you're going to see the glory clean.

00:27:20.800 --> 00:27:27.599
He's going to have more energy than he's ever had before.

00:27:31.419 --> 00:27:35.760
The Lord says, 'I'm going to give him a fountain of youth inside of his blood.

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:40.594
And I'm going to cleanse his arteries.

00:27:40.594 --> 00:27:47.680
' There's a cleansing of plaque in his arteries.

00:27:47.680 --> 00:27:53.421
Because of this new blood flow, he's going to have a brand new start.

00:27:53.421 --> 00:28:00.159
He's going to feel more youth than he's ever had, for he's been tired.

00:28:00.159 --> 00:28:09.954
And He's going to give him a fresh new Holy Ghost fire on his blood.

00:28:09.954 --> 00:28:15.519
It's happening right now as we speak.

00:28:21.380 --> 00:28:26.240
A fresh new fire on John Kilpatrick's blood over his arteries, his neck, and the flow.

00:28:26.240 --> 00:28:34.791
He'll have more energy than he's ever had, and he'll live long and finish strong.

00:28:34.791 --> 00:28:41.691
He'll see the coming of the Lord.

00:28:41.691 --> 00:28:52.799
I hear the Lord say he's not going home; he's going to live long and finish strong into his older age.

00:28:52.799 --> 00:28:56.754
He's going to do this with these older generals.

00:29:07.029 --> 00:29:07.520
I see it so clear.

00:29:07.520 --> 00:29:15.760
There's glory going through his veins right now: his heart, his arteries, and his legs.

00:29:15.760 --> 00:29:20.576
He needs strength in his legs and his knees.

00:29:20.576 --> 00:29:35.897
I see strength in his calves and his thighs so he can stand up and preach longer, for these services will last longer.

00:29:35.897 --> 00:29:40.520
He's renewing everything—a Holy Ghost fire going through his body.

00:29:42.653 --> 00:29:44.569
And this will go through his wife, too.

00:29:44.569 --> 00:29:52.016
They'll be acting like their youth, chasing each other around the house like new kids.

00:29:52.016 --> 00:29:54.140
'Hey, I feel good today!

00:29:54.140 --> 00:29:55.760
' and a youth.

00:29:55.760 --> 00:30:04.240
But He said, 'The glory sustained Moses, and the glory will sustain my elders today.

00:30:04.240 --> 00:30:12.274
' The glory will sustain the elders like I sustained Moses.

00:30:12.274 --> 00:30:20.239
His body didn't grow old; his eyes didn't fade because the glory was on Moses.

00:30:20.239 --> 00:30:28.960
I'm going to do that with my elders; I need them as pioneers of faith.

00:30:28.960 --> 00:30:42.240
Now, some of them don't want to yield to it and they're going to go home.

00:30:48.320 --> 00:30:52.240
But there are certain ones I need as key figures for what's about to come.

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:59.955
They've lived it once, and they'll know what to do with it again.

00:30:59.955 --> 00:31:08.559
I'm going to give them a new mindset concerning this.

00:31:08.559 --> 00:31:17.190
Things they messed up with in the past, they won't repeat.

00:31:17.190 --> 00:31:28.947
They'll come with a fresh vision and fresh outlook on what I'm about to do.

00:31:43.680 --> 00:31:44.160
And he's going to visit the islands throughout Hawaii.

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:47.567
All the islands are glowing with the glory.

00:31:47.567 --> 00:31:53.520
There's a key church in Honolulu—there's a key church in Honolulu.

00:31:54.640 --> 00:32:00.098
